{"tid":490340,"cid":22,"subCid":0,"title":"點解部電腦會突然上唔到網？","createTime":"2017-12-05T13:58:56.000Z","updateTime":"2017-12-05T14:24:07.000Z","uid":149844,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":6,"replies":[{"pid":"3e1fea59a2619339fa9211426d43eb864e287d46","tid":490340,"uid":149844,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-05T13:58:56.000Z","msg":"事情是這樣的<br />\n我朋友部電腦成日都會突然間上唔到網<br />\n咁佢就叫我上去佢度睇下啦<br />\n佢一開機都好好地用區域連線上到一陣網<br />\n大概會上到15分鐘左右 好彩啲就用到30分鐘<br />\n但之後佢就會無啦啦變左<br />\n有限或無法連線（黃色三角形加！感嘆號)<br />\n電腦就接router<br />\n我睇佢啲驅動程式（得一個蟹仔驅動）都正常既<br />\nRealtek PCIe GBE Family Controller<br />\n電腦網絡卡就係onboard蟹仔卡<br />\n<br />\n佢電話用WiFi就好順暢<br />\n唔會話斷下斷下咁既<br />\n有無巴打知點解會咁?"},{"pid":"b8ed97cfe5e6e2265a7ae6932e8a14af2a075e55","tid":490340,"uid":149844,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-05T14:01:55.000Z","msg":"求學野"},{"pid":"b7bc0d21b7968e4d6a0499b31aa3ae1071bfd5b6","tid":490340,"uid":35507,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-05T14:03:45.000Z","msg":"Router 出事<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"794f4795d1c0f56e04707ad5fb05ea040eaa50d9","tid":490340,"uid":88710,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-05T14:04:21.000Z","msg":"我部舊腦都係咁 上網一陣就會出！號 你fd部機laptop定座枱？"},{"pid":"19d4a085875bce39bce63794ba2a7608d5220e37","tid":490340,"uid":149844,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-05T14:04:49.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>我部舊腦都係咁 上網一陣就會出！號 你fd部機laptop定座枱？</blockquote><br />\n舊式台機"},{"pid":"78b4ee6b2e28eb26bd8d0c6e2231decce93a122c","tid":490340,"uid":88710,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-05T14:05:24.000Z","msg":"啫係用LAN線？"},{"pid":"6ac5ff33f4e7aebae0fd3237127d25d8d6f61a71","tid":490340,"uid":149844,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-05T14:06:29.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>Router 出事<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n係咪有啲咩未set好<br />\n佢用電話上網 好順暢"},{"pid":"a1e888d86f595f3354828b6943c2ccd77612bf6e","tid":490340,"uid":149844,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-05T14:06:39.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>啫係用LAN線？</blockquote><br />\n係"},{"pid":"38b416c2871e084f3f9ad44945252f1d60e251db","tid":490340,"uid":88710,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-05T14:07:02.000Z","msg":"有冇重插過條線？"},{"pid":"72fd590e09438f15852b0806f4071979838dfaf4","tid":490340,"uid":19005,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-05T14:07:34.000Z","msg":"問題係咁撚多朋友出事<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/@.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4012b6810d8316d0a4f65a900b704f80bf64318e","tid":490340,"uid":149844,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-05T14:07:37.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>有冇重插過條線？</blockquote><br />\n有"},{"pid":"159302681e50d7352369d5d03fd3abbd2c4b76de","tid":490340,"uid":88710,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-05T14:09:52.000Z","msg":"我覺得應該都係部腦既問題 實質係咩都研究唔到<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 網上就算搵呢個問題都只係話介面卡問題...但Windows既網路診斷基本上都冇作用<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />所以我覺得純粹係部腦老化既問題<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/banghead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"56aa4c1b04ccf9f92c6a7b8bb2f854ba2bc6b100","tid":490340,"uid":149844,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-05T14:10:35.000Z","msg":"拔左變紅叉<br />\n之後loading<br />\nLoad完都係會去返黃色感嘆號"},{"pid":"a2974afb9f3389be66aa2197ab57ed10f259109b","tid":490340,"uid":23094,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-05T14:10:46.000Z","msg":"WAN線直插有問題嗰部電腦<br />\n乜事都冇-&gt;Router問題<br />\n問題照舊-&gt;換過條線再試吓<br />\n    -&gt;乜事都冇-&gt;線問題<br />\n    -&gt;問題照舊-&gt;Call ISP上門搞<br />\n<br />\n如果係Router問題-&gt;Reset Router<br />\n乜事都冇-&gt;揾個真係識Set Router嘅人幫手Set<br />\n問題照舊-&gt;換Router"},{"pid":"238d1ea1ce5533897152c6950892a30683f397fc","tid":490340,"uid":64290,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-05T14:11:52.000Z","msg":"重開router?"},{"pid":"b4109b2c4aef6e00649833a960d18cc880ed4212","tid":490340,"uid":64290,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-05T14:13:09.000Z","msg":"會唔會係撞ip之類"},{"pid":"85dc5441172e4861abdb3cce4af1fb4a8464a8e9","tid":490340,"uid":149844,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-05T14:20:56.000Z","msg":"我就得問題都大致上得三個<br />\n1. Router有野set錯左/或者壞左<br />\n但係如果router 壞左就應該唔會有得用電話上網<br />\n或者可能佢部分壞<br />\n<br />\n2.線材問題<br />\nLan線壞左<br />\n但如果壞lan線就應該唔會有頭個十幾分鐘上到網<br />\n<br />\n3.主機板網路卡老化<br />\n依個唔知點check<br />\n最多買個張lan card解決<br />\n<br />\n但真係唔知咩問題"},{"pid":"5ad42faad642813188130481c53838235489bbfb","tid":490340,"uid":149844,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-05T14:22:25.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>我覺得應該都係部腦既問題 實質係咩都研究唔到<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 網上就算搵呢個問題都只係話介面卡問題...但Windows既網路診斷基本上都冇作用<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />所以我覺得純粹係部腦老化既問題<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/banghead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n個網路診斷咩作用<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"1fa0d88bb978b03e56c7fdffedcde1666086f42f","tid":490340,"uid":149844,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-05T14:23:10.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>我覺得應該都係部腦既問題 實質係咩都研究唔到<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 網上就算搵呢個問題都只係話介面卡問題...但Windows既網路診斷基本上都冇作用<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />所以我覺得純粹係部腦老化既問題<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/banghead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n個網路診斷<span style=\"color: red;\">無</span>咩作用<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote>"},{"pid":"40020f1146aac4bb891a7338893f3174da501a71","tid":490340,"uid":149844,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-05T14:24:07.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>WAN線直插有問題嗰部電腦<br />\n乜事都冇-&gt;Router問題<br />\n問題照舊-&gt;換過條線再試吓<br />\n    -&gt;乜事都冇-&gt;線問題<br />\n    -&gt;問題照舊-&gt;Call ISP上門搞<br />\n<br />\n如果係Router問題-&gt;Reset Router<br />\n乜事都冇-&gt;揾個真係識Set Router嘅人幫手Set<br />\n問題照舊-&gt;換Router</blockquote><br />\n <br />\n好 我試下先"}]}